# Foundry compendium packs use LevelDB-style numbered `*.log` files as live data
# segments. Ignoring them can drop pack content changes from commits.
# packs/**/LOG*
# packs/**/MANIFEST*
# packs/**/CURRENT
# packs/**/LOCK
# packs/**/000*
# packs/**/*.sst

# packs/**/*.old
# packs/**/*.bak

AGENTS.md
